# 1. IMPLEMENT TRUE DOMAIN-DRIVEN DESIGN (DDD)

The current modules are good but should evolve into true business domains.

Each domain must become self-contained.

Each domain should contain:

* entities
* aggregates
* value objects
* repositories
* services
* factories
* mappers
* DTOs
* validators
* permissions
* policies
* events
* commands
* queries
* hooks
* APIs
* tests

Example:

modules/
vehicle/
entities/
aggregates/
value-objects/
repositories/
services/
factories/
events/
commands/
queries/
dto/
validators/
permissions/
policies/
api/
hooks/
tests/

Business logic must stay inside its domain.

No duplicated logic.

No cross-domain coupling.

